\id JAS - Mbula
\h Jemis
\toc3 Jem
\toc2 Jemis
\toc1 Jemis
\mt2 Cauterǝa nǝ ban
\mt1 JEMIS
\imt1 Mǝncau
\im \bk Cautera mala Jemis\bk* mǝ'eam Mǝtalabangŋo Yesu ka, gilǝì a nre ka pǝlǝa lumi-ine-bwamdǝ-tongno aban ká lumi tongno a nzǝm lo mala Yesu a ɓembe (45-50 AD). Jemis gilǝ cauterǝa mǝnia ka ace amǝ Yahudi mǝnana amǝkpata Yesu na, mǝnana patanni mesǝkia arǝ aban ɗàngɗáng a bum ɓanza ka. À gilǝì ace lǝmdǝì akǝrǝsta njar mǝnana ɓoaro ɓǝà dum nǝi, aɓa do mǝnana nǝ̀ pwasǝ bum Ɓakuli, aɓalǝ atúró malea kat a ban aɓwana ka. Mǝno ka nǝ̀ lǝmdǝ ama à pana ɓamuria nǝ mǝsǝcau a ban Mǝtalabangŋo Yesu. Amǝɓalle ka à kǝ ɓak ɓabumia ɓǝà alta sǝlǝe mala Ɓakuli, sǝ ɓǝà lidǝmba nǝ do pa ɓamuru a ban Yesu, ko ɓǝà nda aɓa kārǝkiban ngga. Cau mǝgule aɓalǝi ka nda mana ama paɓamuru mǝ'mǝsǝcau nì kǝ lǝmdǝ rǝì aɓa earcearǝu. Jemis bang ama paɓamuru mǝnana pà nǝ̀ kánǝ ɓwa arǝ pakki atúró mǝɓoarne raka, mǝɓane na. Kǝ ɓuaki arǝ amǝkwaɗi ɓǝà ok cau mala Ɓakuli sǝ ɓǝà kpata cê. Jemis kǝ kwarkir amǝɓal mǝnia yì malǝmce ka ɓǝà dum nǝ munyi ko ɓǝ̀ lang sǝ tanni andǝ kārǝkiban kumia ka, sǝ ɓǝà pa ɓamuria a ban Ɓakuli aɓa hiwi.
\iot Agir mǝnana aɓalǝi ka
\io1 Zǝmba, a ban Ɓakuli ace sǝlǝe andǝ munyi\ior 1:1-18\ior*
\io1 Lǝmdǝ pa ɓamuru mǝnana mǝɓane na raka\ior 1:19--2:26\ior*
\io1 Tsǝkiru arǝ cau mana purkiyi a kun ngga andǝ do nǝ súrǝè\ior 3:1--5:6\ior*
\io1 Do munyi, andǝ cauɓoarna, andǝ hiwi\ior 5:7-20\ior*
\c 1
\s1 Makkun
\p 
\v 1 Mim Jemis, guro mala Ɓakuli andǝ mala Mǝtalabangŋo Yesu Kǝrǝsti, mǝ nda ban terǝ cau aban ká a ban amǝkpata Kǝrǝsti mǝnana aɓalǝ atau lum-nong-ɓari mala amǝ Isǝrayila, mǝnana à mesǝkea arǝ anzali aɓa ɓanza ka. Ən nggǝ makka wun kun!\f + \fr 1:1 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Mat 13:55; Mar 6:3; Atúró 15:13; Gal 1:19\xt*\ft .\f*
\s1 Do nǝ paɓamuru andǝ gandǝrǝu
\p 
\v 2 Wun amǝ'eambǝam, ɓǝ̀ wu kutio aɓalǝ akārǝkiban ɗàngɗáng ngga, ɓǝ̀ ban ɓoara wun kǝ̀rkǝ́r,
\v 3 acemǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu cam kàngkàng aɓa kārǝkiban ngga, paɓamuru ma'wun nǝ̀ lidǝmba nǝ rǝcandǝa.
\v 4 Wu lidǝmba nǝ came kàngkàng, wu kǝa kpa ɗang, acemǝnana ɓǝ̀ ɓeal wun pa kǝla mǝnana Ɓakuli kǝ earce kat ka, wu kǝa gatti ɗang.
\p 
\v 5 Ɓǝ̀ kǝɓwa aɓalǝ wun ɗwanyi sǝlǝe ace pak mǝɓoarne ka, ɓǝ̀ zǝmba a ban Ɓakuli mǝnana kǝ pa nǝ ɓabumi kat nggwani pà kàm raka. Sǝ à nǝ̀ pè wi.
\v 6 Ɓǝ̀ zǝmbi wi nǝ ɓabumi mwashat, ɓǝ̀ kǝa pak nǝ ɓukkibum ɗang, acemǝnana ɓwa mana ɓabumi kǝ ɗǝnggǝli ka nda kǝla gung nggeamùr mǝnana kǝ came a ban mǝ'mwashati raka.
\v 7 Ulang mǝnia yì ɓwa ka ɓǝ̀ kǝa tsǝk ɓālǝi ama nǝ̀ ak kǝgìr a bu Mǝtalabangŋo Ɓakuli ɗang;
\v 8 yì ka, ɓwa na, ɗenyicau male gakkia, kǝ tamsǝ kusǝì amur kǝgìr mwashat ɗang.
\p 
\v 9 Mǝ'eamrǝarǝu mǝnana mǝ'tǝ̀r na ka ɓǝ̀ pak banɓoarnado acemǝnana Ɓakuli kǝ twali nǝ gulo kǝ̀rkǝ́r.
\v 10 Sǝ mǝ'eamrǝarǝu mǝnana mǝkume na ka ɓǝ̀ jali aɓa kyamsǝɓamuri, acemǝnana yì ka, nǝ̀ ime nǝ̀ sukkio kǝla pwasǝo bondo.\f + \fr 1:10 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Isha 40:6-7\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 11 Ɓǝ̀ pwari ta ka, kǝ pisǝ abondo sǝ pwasǝia kǝ sukkio, ɓoarjam malea kǝ kiɗìkì. Anggo gbal, mǝkume nǝ̀ ueɓà andǝ atúró male.
\s1 Tsǝkbu mana à kǝ kumi // ace kārǝkiban ngga
\p 
\v 12 Ɓakuli nǝ̀ tsǝkbu amur ɓwa mǝnana dum nǝ mǝsǝcau a baní aɓa kārǝkiban mana yiu amur paɓamuru male ka. Acemǝnana ɓǝ̀ camǝna kàngkàng ngga, a masǝlǝate ka nǝ̀ kum tangnakusǝu mala yilǝmu mǝnana Ɓakuli pacau ama nǝ̀ pea aɓwana mǝnana à lǝmdǝì wi earcearǝu ka.
\v 13 Ɓǝ̀ kārǝkiban yipì ɓwa ka ɓǝ̀ kǝa na ama, Ɓakuli na kǝ kārǝki ka ɗàng. Acemǝnana Ɓakuli ka à pà nǝ̀ kārǝki nǝ ɓealɓikea ɗang, sǝ yì ka, kǝ kārǝki kǝɓwa gbal ɗàng.\f + \fr 1:13 \fq Acemǝnana Ɓakuli ka à pà nǝ̀ kārǝki nǝ ɓealɓikea ɗang, sǝ yì ka, kǝ kārǝki kǝɓwa gbal ɗàng \ft Ko: <<Ɓakuli ka à pà nǝ̀ gandǝ swárè nǝ mǝɓike ɗàng, sǝ yì ka, kǝ swár kǝɓwa nǝ̀ kánǝi aɓa mǝɓike ɗàng.>>\f*
\v 14 Sǝama koyan ngga kǝ kutio a kārǝkiban yi mǝnana ɓǝ̀ suno male swárǝni, ɓosǝna kusǝì ka.
\v 15 Sǝ ɓǝ̀ suno gongŋǝna ka kǝ ɓǝl atúró mala cauɓikea, sǝ ɓǝ̀ cauɓikea gulna ka nǝ̀ ɓǝl lú.
\p 
\v 16 Wun amǝ'eamrǝarǝu mǝnana ǝn earkiyi acea raka, ɓǝà kǝa swarki wun ɗàng.
\v 17 Koya ɓoro mǝɓoarne, mǝɓafoe ka, sulǝ nǝ kuli, nǝban Ɓakuli Tárrú mǝnana pak atǎlaban\f + \fr 1:17 \fq atǎlaban: \ft À nda ka pwari, andǝ zongŋo, andǝ anlero kat.\f* ngga, mǝnana ɓǝ̀ pǝlǝa aya buì ka kǝ nggaɗi ɗang sǝ kǝ túr pǝndǝa raka\f + \fr 1:17 \fq kǝ nggaɗi ɗang sǝ kǝ túr pǝndǝa raka: \ft Ko <<kǝ nggaɗiki bancame andǝ pa male kǝla yilǝmi gir raka.>>\f*.
\v 18 Aɓa kàne male sǝ yi ɓǝl sǝm nǝ cau mǝ'mǝsǝcau nì; tàr sǝm atà dǝmbe aɓalǝ aɓwana mǝnana pusǝia kat ka.\f + \fr 1:18 \fqa Earna nǝi aɓa kane male sǝ twal sǝm ɓǝ̀ sǝm duk aɓwana ace ɓamúrì, ace mani ka yi tasǝ cau male mǝ'mǝsǝcau nì ɓǝ̀ yi pa sǝm bǝsa ɓǝlban.\f*
\s1 Ok cau andǝ pe
\p 
\v 19 Wun amǝ'eambam aɓa earcearǝu, wu parkir wun arǝ mǝnia ka: koyan ngga ɓǝ̀ kaurǝa ta ok cau, ɓǝ̀ dǝndi arǝ nacau, sǝ ɓǝ̀ dǝndi arǝ pak bumlulla.
\v 20 Acemǝnana ɓǝ̀ bumo lul ka a pà nǝ gandǝ pak gìr mǝɓoarne mǝnana Ɓakuli earce ɓǝà pè ka ɗàng.
\v 21 Ace mani ka wu bwaki bu wun arǝ koya ulang gìr ɓeami andǝ nggaman ɓealɓikea, sǝ wu ak cau mala Ɓakuli mǝnana à pandǝi a ɓabum wun, mǝnana nǝ̀ amsǝ wun ngga, nǝ nyesǝmuru.
\v 22 Wu duk aɓwana mǝnana à kǝ ok cau sǝ à kǝ tsǝì aɓa túró ka, wu kǝa duk amǝ oe nǝ kiru nǝmurǝì ɗàng. Mǝno ka wu nda ban swarki ɓamur rǝ wun. Wu pak gìr mǝnana ce nì bang ngga.
\v 23 Ɓwa mǝnana kǝ ok cau mala Ɓakuli sǝ kǝ tsǝì aɓa túró raka, nda kǝla ɓwa mǝnana kǝ sǝn ɓamǝsǝi a tapwari ka,
\v 24 anzǝm mǝnana sǝnǝna ɓamǝsǝi sǝ kutina umna ka, kara ɓālǝi lorǝna ko lang sǝ ɓamǝsǝi pa.
\v 25 Sǝ ɓwa mǝnana kǝ tsǝkiri pepè arǝ bǝlki ɓalǝ anggurcau mǝɓafoe mala Ɓakuli mǝnana kǝ panzǝban ngga, sǝ ɓǝ̀ lidǝmba, ɓālǝi lórǝ́ cau mǝnana ok raka, Ɓakuli nǝ̀ tsǝki wi bu aɓa gìr mǝnana pakkiyi ka.
\p 
\v 26 Ɓǝ̀ kǝɓwa kǝ ne ɓamúrì ama yì ka, mǝkpata Ɓakuli na, sǝ bwal kúni raka, ɓwarkina aɓa ɗenyicau male. Kpata Ɓakuli male ka mǝɓane na.
\v 27 Kwaɗi mǝɓoarnsari, mǝɓafoe mǝnana Ɓakuli Tár sǝm earkiyice ka, nda tsǝkir akáwá andǝ amā-lú aɓalǝ atanni malea, andǝ ɓanggi pǝndǝkiban mala ɓanza.
\c 2
\s1 Wu nying lǝmdǝ tàrban
\p 
\v 1 Wun amǝ'eambǝam mǝnana wu pana ɓamur wun aban Mǝtalabangŋo Yesu Kǝrǝsti, mana lùmsǝ nǝ tǎlaban ngga, wu nying lǝmdǝ tàrban.
\v 2 Ɓǝà twali ama ɓeɓwa kútí aban kpapi ma'wun, sǝ ɓwe ka oasǝ girmunabu zǝnariya andǝ agir-nggūrǝu mǝɓoarne arǝì. Sǝ ɓeɓwa man ngga kutio nǝ asanggina gir mǝpǝndǝke arǝì.
\v 3 Wun nǝ̀ tsǝkir ɓwa mǝnana oasǝ agir-nggūrǝu mǝɓoarne ka, wun nǝ̀ pe wi ban-do mǝɓoarne, sǝ mala mǝ'tǝ̀r ka wun ne wi ama, <<Came akaná>> ko ana raka, <<Duk kani a nzali>> ka le?
\v 4 Ɓǝ̀ wu pak anggo ka, wu lǝmdǝ ma tàrban aɓalǝ wun re? Sǝ ɗǝm ngga ɓǝ̀ wu pak anggo ka, wu pa aban lǝmdǝ ama wu nda ban ɓashi arǝ wun nǝ ɓabum mǝɓike re?
\v 5 Wu kwakikir wun, wun amǝ'eamrǝarǝu mǝnana ǝn earkiyi acea raka, Ɓakuli twal aɓwana mǝnana amǝɓanza nyesǝia amǝ'tǝ̀r na ka, ɓǝa duk amǝkume aɓa paɓamuru a baní. Sǝ ɗǝm ngga ɓǝa kum domurǝm mǝnana Ɓakuli pàcau ama nǝ̀ pe aɓwana mǝnana à kǝ earce ka.
\v 6 Sǝ wun ngga wu twal amǝ'tǝ̀r a kun kǝgìr ɗang. Nggearǝì ka amǝkume na mǝnana à pakiyia wun tanni, à nungiyi wun aban ká a ndaɓashi ka re?
\v 7 À nda ka kǝ aɓwana mǝnana à kǝ na mǝɓane amur lullǝu mǝɓoarne mala Yesu Kǝrǝsti mǝnana à tunǝkina wun nǝi ka re?
\p 
\v 8 Ɓǝ̀ ɓafo na wu bwalǝna mǝnia yì nggurcau mala murǝm Ɓakuli, mǝnana à gilǝì aɓa Malǝmce ka, ama <<Wu earce ɓio-mǝ'njarmurkala kǝla mǝnana a earce ɓamuro ka,>> wu nǝ̀ nggǝ pak mǝɓoarne.\f + \fr 2:8 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pǝris 19:18\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 9 Sǝa ma ɓǝ̀ wu kǝ lǝmdǝ tàrban ngga, wu nda rǝ pak cauɓikea, sǝ wu yàlni nggurcau mǝno.
\v 10 Acemǝnana ɓwa mana bwal anggurcau mala Ɓakuli kat, sǝ yàllî mwashat ka, yàlni anggurcau kat.
\v 11 Ɓakuli mǝnana na ama, ɓǝa kǝa nongginǝ-rǝarǝu raka, kǝ nda na ama ɓǝa kǝa wal-lú raka. Ko ɓǝ̀ a nda mǝ'nongginǝ-rǝarǝu raka, sǝ a kǝ wal-lú ka, a dumǝna mǝyàli nggurcau.\f + \fr 2:11 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pur 20:13; Nggur 5:17,18\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 12 Ace mani ka, ɓǝ̀ mana kat wu nǝ̀ na, ko wu nǝ̀ pak ka, wu ɗenyi ama à nǝ̀ pakka wun ɓashi nǝ nggurcau mǝnana kǝ panzǝ sǝm ngga.
\v 13 Ɓǝ̀ yiua pak ɓashi ka, à pà nǝ̀ sǝn mǝsǝswatǝr mala aɓwana mǝnana à kǝ lǝmdǝ mǝsǝswatǝr aban acilia aɓwana raka ɗang; sǝ ɓwa mǝnana kǝ lǝmdǝ mǝsǝswatǝr ka Ɓakuli nǝ̀ lǝmdǝì wi mǝsǝswatǝr a pwari ɓashi!
\s1 Paɓamuru aban Yesu andǝ // pakki atúró mǝɓoarne
\p 
\v 14 Mana nda ɓoaro male, wun amǝ'eamrǝarǝu, mǝnana ɓǝ̀ ɓwa na ama pana ɓamuru aban Yesu, sǝ lǝmdǝí aɓa pakki atúró male raka? Mǝno yì paɓamuru ka nǝ̀ amsǝi le?
\v 15 Ɓǝ̀ do ama ɓe mǝ'eamrǝarǝu ɓwabura ko ɓwama na aɓalǝ wun, sǝ pànǝ agir-nggūrǝu ko girlina ɗang.
\v 16 Ɓǝ̀ ɓeɓwa atà wun ne wi ama, <<Kyan jam, ɓǝ̀ Ɓakuli tsǝko bu, wu kum gir-koarǝu sǝ wu ɗǝmbǝo,>> sǝ pè wi gìr mǝnana ɓoaro ɓǝ̀ pàng nǝi ace nggūrǝì raka, mana nda ɓoaro male?
\v 17 Anggo gbal, ɓǝ̀ paɓamuru pa atārǝia andǝ túró raka, nda ɓà.
\p 
\v 18 Sǝa ma ɓǝ̀ ɓwa nǝ̀ na ama, <<A ndanǝ paɓamuru sǝ mǝ ndanǝ atúró.>> Lǝmdǝam paɓamuru mô mǝnana pànǝ atúró atè raka, sǝ mǝ nǝ lǝmdǝo paɓamuru mem aban Ɓakuli nǝ atúró mǝɓoarne mem.
\v 19 A ear ama Ɓakuli na mwashat; a pangŋa pepe. Sǝ ko nggearǝ akukwar gbal ka à earǝna nǝ mǝnia, sǝ rǝia kǝ ɓǝla ace ɓangciu.
\v 20 We gǝm ɓwa, a kǝ earce ɓǝa lǝmdǝo ama paɓamuru mǝnana atúró mǝɓoarne pa atè raka mǝɓane na le?
\v 21 Kà-sǝm Ibǝrayim ngga, pa ace túró mǝnana pa, mǝnana yi pa ɓoro nǝ muni Ishaku amur gyangŋan ngga, sǝ Ɓakuli twali mǝ'cauɓoarna na ka re?\f + \fr 2:21 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Tite 22:1-14\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 22 Wu sǝni ka, paɓamuru male andǝ atúró male ka à kǝ gya atārǝia. Nǝ atúró sǝ paɓamuru male lùmsǝo.
\v 23 Sǝ cau mǝnana Malǝmce bangŋi ama, <<Ibǝrayim earnǝ cau mala Ɓakuli, sǝ Ɓakuli lǝmdǝí mǝ'cauɓoarna na>> ka, yi duk mǝsǝcau, nda sǝ à tunǝi ama gyajam mala Ɓakuli ka.\f + \fr 2:23 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Tite 15:6; 2Kpa 20:7; Isha 41:8\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 24 Wu sǝni, Ɓakuli kǝ twal ɓwa mǝ'cauɓoarna na ace atúró male, pa ace paɓamuru nǝmurǝì ɗang.
\v 25 Anggo gbal sǝ Rahap mā-gyatarǝu ka, Ɓakuli e mǝ'cauɓoarna na ace atúró, acemǝnana ak Amǝ Isǝrayila mana à túriá ace shenzǝ nzali ka a ɓala male, sǝ kya pusǝia nǝ ɓe njar ɗàng sǝ à au ka.\f + \fr 2:25 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Jes 2:1-21\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 26 Kǝla mǝnana dǝɓang'rǝu mǝnana yilǝmu pa aɓalǝi raka lú na ka, anggo gbal paɓamuru mǝnana kǝ lǝmdǝ rǝì aɓa túró raka lune na.
\c 3
\s1 Bwal lasǝu
\p 
\v 1 Wun amǝ'eamrǝarǝu, bangula wun ɓǝa kǝa duk amǝkànìgìr aban kpapi mala amǝkwaɗi ɗang, kǝla mǝnana wu sǝlǝna ka, sǝm amǝkani cau mala Ɓakuli ka, ɓashi ma'sǝm aban Ɓakuli ka nǝ̀ candǝe nǝ̀ yàllî mala acili aɓwana.
\v 2 Acemǝnana sǝm kat ka sǝm nggǝ ɓwarkio arǝ anjar pas. Ɓǝ̀ ɓwa kǝ ɓwarki aɓalǝ acau male raka, man yì ɓwa ka lùmsǝ̀nà ɓwa, mǝnana nǝ̀ gandǝi nǝ̀ bwal ɓamúrì a koya njar kat ka.
\v 3 Sǝm nggǝ oasǝi apǝr nggwiandan a kunia ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ sǝm cia ɓǝa oka sǝm, sǝ sǝm nggǝ pǝlǝ múrià aban mǝnana kat sǝm earce ɓǝa pǝlǝ kam ngga.
\v 4 Sǝni, kat andǝ gulo mala waru-bǝsa mǝnana nggea-gung mǝcandǝe na kǝ ging nǝi ka, mǝgara samsǝa na à kǝ pūrǝí nǝi aban o aban mǝnana mǝtawaru earce nǝ̀ ká nǝi kam ngga.
\v 5 Anggo gbal, lasǝu ka gir mǝkyauwe na aɓa nggūrǝu, sǝ kǝ gandǝ jali amur agir mǝgulke.
\p Wu sǝni, mǝlasǝ bǝsa bǝti kǝ pisǝ nggea nkwarki dalǝm.
\v 6 Nggearǝ lasǝ ɓwapǝndǝa gbal ka lasǝ bǝsa na, ɓanza mala ɓealɓikea na aɓa nggūrǝ sǝm, nyar ɗǝm ngga kǝ kiɗiki ɓwa kǝring. Lasǝu ɗǝm ngga kǝ kiɗiki ɓwa aɓa do male kat, sǝ yì ka, bǝsa ɓá tūli-lú na kǝ earki nǝi ka.
\p 
\v 7 Ɓwapǝndǝa nǝ̀ gandǝ bwalmúr agirkusǝu kat; anyal, agir mǝnana à kǝ pūrǝ nǝ bumia a nzali, andǝ agir mǝnana nǝ yilǝmu aɓa nggeamùr ka. Ɓwapǝndǝa kǝ gandǝ ɓungia sǝ nǝ̀ tsǝia ɓǝà oki wi.
\v 8 Sǝ kǝɓwa pà kàm nǝ̀ gandǝ bwalmúr lasǝu ɗang. Ndanǝ songnǝo sǝ lùmsǝ nǝ ɓealɓikea andǝ barya mǝnana nǝ̀ wal-lú ka.
\v 9 Nǝ́ lasǝ sǝm sǝ sǝm nggǝ ɓwangsǝ Mǝtalabangŋo mǝnana nda Tár sǝm ngga. Sǝ nǝ́ kǝ lasǝuî sǝ sǝm nggǝ sú aɓwana mǝnana Ɓakuli pea aɓa nggūrǝì ka.
\v 10 Nǝ́ kun sǝ sǝm nggǝ ɓwangsǝban, sǝ nǝ́ kun sǝ sǝm nggǝ súban. Wun amǝ'eambǝam, ɓoaro ɓǝ̀ pa anggo ɗang!
\v 11 Mǝsǝcau ka, mur mǝɓoarne andǝ mur mǝ'nkaunkauni kǝ pur a mǝsǝmur mǝ'mwashati ɗang.
\v 12 Wun amǝ'eambǝam, nggun vwari pa nǝ̀ pusǝ ɓǝla mpandimuru ɗang, sǝ nggun ɓau pa nǝ̀ pusǝ vwari ɗang. Mǝsǝmur mǝnana nda nkaunkaun ngga pa nǝ̀ pà mur mǝɓoarne ɗang.
\s1 Sǝlǝe mǝnana pur nǝ kuli ka
\p 
\v 13 Ɓǝ̀ wu ndanǝ sǝlǝe sǝ wu sùrǝ́nà rǝ anjargula mala Ɓakuli ka, wu lǝmdǝí aɓa do mǝɓoarne, wu kǝ pak atúró mǝɓoarne nǝ nyesǝɓamuru mǝnana kǝ pur aɓa sǝlǝe ka.
\v 14 Sǝ ɓǝ̀ wu lùmsǝ nǝ mɓali, andǝ ɓinǝmuru, andǝ earce ɓamuru a ɓabum wun ngga, wu ɗeki nggori, wu kǝa gìr mǝsǝcau nǝ nyir ɗang.
\v 15 Acemǝnana mɓali andǝ earce ɓamuru ka à pa aɓa sǝlǝe mǝnana mala Ɓakuli na ka ɗang. Amǝno yì agir ka à mala ɓanza na, mala Bangŋo mala Ɓakuli na ɗang; mala mgbǝrǝm na.
\v 16 Ban mǝnana kat mɓali andǝ earce ɓamuru nda kam ngga, abanì sǝ awu nǝ kum zurǝki andǝ koya ɓealɓikea.
\p 
\v 17 Sǝ sǝlǝe mǝnana pur nǝ kuli ka mǝɓoarnsari na, sǝ ndanǝ earce dotarǝu, nda ɓukɓuk aɓa pa male, kǝ ɗenyi nǝ aɓwana, lùmsǝ nǝ mǝsǝswatǝr andǝ atúró mǝɓoarne, kǝ lǝmdǝ tàrban ɗang sǝ kǝ pak gìr aɓa mǝsǝcau.
\v 18 Aɓwana mǝnana amǝ yinǝ dotarǝu na aɓa rǝpwala ka, atúró malea nǝ̀ tsǝk aɓwana ɓǝà kǝ pak agir mǝɓoarne mǝnana Ɓakuli earkiyicea ka.
\c 4
\s1 Pa ɓamuru a ban Ɓakuli
\p 
\v 1 Mana gir nì na yiki nǝ munǝo, sǝ mana gir nì na yiki nǝ loasǝkiaban aɓalǝ wun ɗe? Asuno ma'wun mala earce banɓoarnado mǝnana à kǝ munǝ a ɓabum wun ngga, à nǝ̀ yiki nǝia re?
\v 2 Wu kǝ earce gìr, sǝ wu kum gìr nî ɗang, ace mani ka, wu kutia wal-lú; wu sham agir mala aɓwana kǝ̀rkǝ́r, sǝ wu gandǝ kumia ɗàng, ace mani ka wu kutia loàsǝ̀ban andǝ munǝo ace mǝnana wu nǝ̀ ea arǝ amǝtalea ka. Wu kǝ kum gìr mǝnana bum wun earce ka ɗàng acemǝnana wu zǝmbi Ɓakuli ɗang.
\v 3 Andǝa zǝmba mǝnana wu zǝm ngga, wu kum ɗang, acemǝnana wu zǝm nǝ ɓabum mǝɓoarne ɗang; zǝmba ma'wun ngga nda ace mǝnana ɓǝà pa wun, wun nǝ̀ lùmsǝ anpel mala ɓamur rǝ wun.
\p 
\v 4 Wun amǝ ɗwanyi do nǝ mǝsǝcau a ban Ɓakuli andǝ doɓala! Wu sǝlǝ mbo ama duk gyajam mala ɓanza ka do ɓibura na arǝ Ɓakuli? Ace mani ka ɓwa mǝnana twalo nǝ̀ pa kǝla mala amǝ'ɓealɓikea ka, dumǝna ɓimǝbura mala Ɓakuli.
\v 5 Ko wu kǝ sǝni kǝla nda ɓà sǝ Ɓakuli bang aɓa Malǝmce male ama: Bangŋo Mǝfele mǝnana tsǝì a ɓabum sǝm ngga earce ɓǝ̀ sǝm kpapì andǝ ɓekǝ gìr ɗàng.
\v 6 Sǝ Ɓakuli ka kǝ pa sǝm ɓwamuru kǝ̀rkǝ́r. Nda gìr mǝnana tsǝa sǝ Malǝmce na ama,
\q1 <<Ɓakuli kǝ ɓinǝ cau mala
\q2 amǝ'twàlɓamúrû,
\q1 sǝ kǝ ɓwamur
\q2 amǝ'nongsǝmúrû.>>\f + \fr 4:6 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pas 3:34\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 7 Ace mani ka wu nyesǝ mur wun a ban Ɓakuli! Wu ɓinǝì Shetan, sǝ yì ka, nǝ̀ ɓanggi ban wun.
\v 8 Wu sungŋo aban Ɓakuli tù sǝ yì gbal ka nǝ̀ sungŋo aban wun tù. Wu ɗeki pakkiagir mǝɓane, wun amǝ'cauɓikea! Wu gilǝki ɗenyicau ma'wun ɓǝ̀ dum nǝ ɓoarnsari, wun aɓwana mǝnana ɓabum wun gaki ka!
\v 9 Ɓǝ̀ ɓabum wun kìɗìkì, wu ɓua, sǝ wu dukdo tímúrû. Ɓǝ̀ oalo ma'wun nyar a doatu, sǝ ɓǝ̀ banɓoarnado ma'wun nyar a tímúrû.
\v 10 Wu nongsǝmur wun a ɓadǝm Mǝtalabangŋo, sǝ yì ka, nǝ̀ gusǝlǝ wun.
\p 
\v 11 Wun amǝ'eambǝam, wu nying twal-lullǝarǝ wun. Ɓwa mǝnana kǝ nacau mǝɓane amur ɓi, ko kǝ kiɗiki ɓi ka, ndaban na mǝɓane amur nggurcau mala Ɓakuli, andǝ ɓashì nggurcau mala Ɓakuli. Sǝ ɓǝ̀ a kǝ ɓashi nggurcau ka, a ndarǝ ɓinǝ kpata nzongcau mala earcearǝu. Anggo ka a ndarǝ na ama a ndanǝ rǝcandǝa mala ɓashì nggurcau mala Ɓakuli.
\v 12 Ɓakuli nda nǝmurǝì pākiyi nggurcau ka, sǝ kǝ yì nda mǝ'ɓashi, yì nda kǝ ɓwa mǝnana ndanǝ rǝcandǝa mala amsǝban ko kiɗikiban ngga. Sǝ we ka, a nda yana mǝnana a nǝ ɓashì ɓio ka?
\s1 Nunkiru amur nggori
\p 
\v 13 Wu kwaki kir wun, wun aɓwana mǝnana wu kǝ na ama, <<Yalung ko li ka sǝm nǝ̀ ká a là mǝnia ko là mǝno, sǝm nǝ̀ nggá pak pǝlǝa mwashat a banì. Sǝm nǝ̀ nggali, sǝm nǝ̀ kum boalo kpǝm>> ngga.
\v 14 Mana gir nì na a súrǝì mǝnana nǝ̀ kumban li ka? Mana nda yilǝmio, mǝnana à nǝ̀ na ama nda a ɓabuo ka? Nda kǝla burambulo mǝnana à nǝ̀ sǝni ado sǝ zuku ka ndǝrmina ka.\f + \fr 4:14 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pas 27:1\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 15 Cau mǝnana ɓoaro ɓǝ́ wun nǝ̀ na ka nda mǝnana ama, <<Ɓǝ̀ Mǝtalabangŋo earǝna, sǝ nying sǝm nǝ yilǝmu ka, sǝm nǝ̀ pak mǝnia ka ko mǝno.>>
\v 16 Sǝ ado ka wu kǝ arkikun wun sǝ wu kǝ nggori aɓa ɗenyicau ma'wun. Sǝ mǝno yì arkikun ngga mǝɓane.
\v 17 Ace mani ka, ɓwa mǝnana súrǝ́nà rǝgir mǝɓoarne mǝnana ɓoaro ɓǝ̀ pa sǝ pè raka, pàngŋǝ̀nà cauɓikea.
\c 5
\s1 Nunkiru amur amǝkume
\p 
\v 1 Wu kwaki kir wun, wun amǝkume! Wu ɓua, wu mak'zwalo, ace akanggǝrang tanni mǝnana à kǝ yiu amur wun ngga.
\v 2 Agǝna ma'wun rǝmǝna, sǝ agir-nggūrǝu ma'wun ngga mburia linia.
\v 3 Agirkuma ma'wun mǝnana à pea nǝ azǝrfa andǝ zǝnariya ka, sásà linia. Sǝ mǝno yì sásà ka nda mǝnana nǝ̀ yinǝ nakún ɓashi amur wun, sǝ nǝ̀ lì nyam wun kǝla bǝsa ka. Wu ramǝni ɓamur rǝ wun gǝna aɓa mǝnia yì ɓanza kǝ ká nǝ ká masǝlǝate ka.\f + \fr 5:3 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Mat 6:19\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 4 Wu sǝni! Aɓwana mǝnana à pakka wun túró a ɓaban sǝ wu ginǝ mbwea ace ɓǝmbǝriban ma'wun ngga, ɓua malea bwalǝna ban Ɓakuli. Aɓwana mǝnana à pakka wun túró pwan girɓaban ngga, ɓua malea warina a kir Mǝtalabangŋo mǝnana Karban kat ka.\f + \fr 5:4 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Nggur 24:14,15\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 5 Wu dumǝna a ɓanza aɓa mǝɓoarne mala kume andǝ liki agir meang'meang mana ɓabum wun earkiyice ka. Wu nda kǝla andá-lǝsǝa mǝ'nyange mǝnana à nǝ̀ nggá pwanmyalia ka.
\v 6 Wu kùmsǝ̀nà kún amǝ'kunpwasǝa a ɓashi, wu walna luia, yia mǝnana à pànǝ kǝ cau arǝ wun raka.
\s1 Domunyi aɓa tanni
\p 
\v 7 Wun amǝ'eamrǝarǝu, wu dum nǝ munyi bà pwari mǝnana Yesu Mǝtalabangŋo nǝ̀ yiu nǝi ka. Wu sǝn domunyi mala mǝ'rya mǝnana kǝ pa aban kundǝ mbulo dǝmba andǝ masǝlǝata mbulo ka. Kǝ dum nǝ tsǝkɓalǝu ace agirɓaban ɓǝà pa ɓǝlea mǝɓoarne.
\v 8 Wun gbal ka, wu dum nǝ munyi sǝ wu cam kàngkàng aɓa ɗenyicau ma'wun, acemǝnana yiu mala Mǝtalabangŋo gbashìnà tù.
\p 
\v 9 Wun amǝ'eamrǝarǝu, wu kǝa nggwani arǝarǝ wun ɗàng, acemǝnana Ɓakuli ɓǝ̀ kǝa ɓasha wun ɗàng. Wu sǝni! Mǝɓashi nda aban came a kunkurǝm!
\p 
\v 10 Wun amǝ'eamrǝarǝu, wu ɗenyi nǝ amǝ'ɓangnǝa mala Ɓakuli mǝnana à yì bang cau aɓa lullǝ Mǝtalabangŋo ka. Ɓǝ̀ domunyi malea aɓa gandǝrǝu aɓata tanni dupa sǝm gìrkànì.
\v 11 Kǝla mǝnana wu sǝlǝ ka, yia mǝnana à lidǝmba nǝ came kàngkàng aɓa paɓamuru malea ka, sǝm twalia amǝ'kúm tsǝkbu mala Ɓakuli na. Wu ongŋǝna ce came mala Ayuba aɓa mǝkwane, sǝ wu sǝna gìr mǝnana Mǝtalabangŋo Ɓakuli pakki wi a masǝlǝate ka. Mǝtalabangŋo ka lùmsǝ nǝ mǝsǝswatǝr andǝ ɓwamuru.\f + \fr 5:11 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Ayu 1:21,22; 2:10; Ang 103:8\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 12 Wun amǝ'eambam, a dǝmba nǝ ko yia gìr ka, wu kǝa kángìr ɗang, ko <<nǝ kuli,>> ko <<nǝ nzali,>> ko nǝ kǝgìr ɗàng. Cau ma'wun ngga ɓǝ̀ kǝa kútì <<E>> ko <<Awo>> ɗàng. Ɓǝ̀ ana raka, ɓashi mala Ɓakuli nǝ̀ bwal wun.\f + \fr 5:12 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Mat 5:34-37\xt*\ft .\f*
\s1 Rǝcandǝa mala hiwi
\p 
\v 13 Kǝ ɓwa aɓalǝ wun kǝ tanni le? Ɓwe ɓǝ̀ pak hiwi. Kǝ ɓwa nda aɓa bumpwasǝa? Ɓwe ɓǝ̀ tu-nggyal ɓwangsǝki Ɓakuli.
\v 14 Kǝ ɓwa atà wun rǝì kǝ pakki wi le? Ɓwe ɓǝ̀ tunǝ aɓwana-mǝgule mala amǝkpata Ɓakuli, ɓǝà pakki wi hiwi, sǝ ɓǝà hasǝi wi mùrú olif amurí aɓa lullǝ Mǝtalabangŋo.\f + \fr 5:14 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Mar 6:13\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 15 Sǝ hiwi mǝnana à pe nǝ ɓabum mwashat ka, nǝ̀ amsǝ mǝrǝkwana ɓǝ̀ nggūrǝì ɓǝ̀ pwalo. Mǝtalabangŋo ka nǝ̀ loasǝi aɓa rǝpina male, sǝ ɓǝ̀ pak cauɓikea ka à nǝ̀ twali wi banì.
\p 
\v 16 Ace mani ka wu banggia rǝwun acauɓikea ma'wun, sǝ wu pakkia rǝwun hiwi, ace mǝnana ɓǝà twala wun ban arǝkwana ma'wun ngga. Hiwi mala mǝɓealɓoarna mǝnana pè nǝ ɓabumi mwashat ka, ndanǝ rǝcandǝa sǝ kǝ pak túró.
\p 
\v 17 Iliya ka ɓwapǝndǝa na kǝla sǝm. Pak hiwi a ɓè pwari nǝ ɓabumi kat ama mbulo ɓǝ̀ kǝa nya ɗang, sǝ mbulo nya a ɓanza ɗang, pǝlǝa tàrú nǝ zongŋo tongno-nong-mwashat.\f + \fr 5:17 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 1Amur 17:1; 18:1,2\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 18 Ɗǝm ngga yi pak hiwi ama mbulo ɓǝ̀ nya, sǝ kùli nya mbulo, nzali pusǝ agirpwala, à pusǝ ɓǝlea.
\s1 Nyesǝ amǝɓwarkio a tanjar
\p 
\v 19 Wun amǝ'eambam, ɓǝ̀ kǝ ɓwa aɓalǝ wun ɓwarki tanjar mala Ɓakuli, wu nyesǝi a tanjar.
\v 20 Wu sǝlǝ ama ɓwa mǝnana nyesǝ mǝ'cauɓikea a tanjar ka, nǝ̀ amsǝ yilǝmi mǝ'cauɓikea man aɓa lú, sǝ nǝ̀ tsǝa Ɓakuli nǝ̀ twalban acauɓikea pas.\f + \fr 5:20 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pas 10:12\xt*\ft .\f*
